This Application is Developed in the Python Language. 
In this application, I used Python Libarys to develop this application. 
Tkinter for used to construct basic graphical user interface (GUI) applications.
Geopy for locating the coordinates of addresses, cities, countries, and landmarks across the globe using third-party geocoders and other data sources.
TimeZoneFinder looks up the corresponding timezone for a given set of coordinates on Earth, entirely offline.
Pytz allows accurate and cross-platform timezone calculations using Python.

and last I used weather API by Open Weather map
